 write a program to read sno,sname,group,3 subjects
    and print total and avg


//To read the marks of three Subjects and Display the Total, Avg and Class
a = int(input("Enter the marks of first subject: "))
b = int(input("Enter the marks of second subject: "))
c = int(input("Enter the marks of third subject: "))
total = a+b+c
avg = total/3
print("Total marks: ",total)
print("Average marks: ",avg)

Output:-
Enter the marks of first subject:84
Enter the marks of second subject:90
Enter the marks of third subject:75
Total marks: 249
Average marks: 83.0
